text: Dhok Padhal () is a village in Jhelum District, Punjab, Pakistan. ==Geography== The village is at 32° 58' 40" North, 73° 30' 40" East and has an altitude of 275 metres (905 ft) Falling Rain Genomics and has an area of about .It lies 10 km west of Dina, 5 km north of Rohtas and 30 km north east of Tilla Jogian. ==Related pages== *Dhok padhal map *school name Category:Villages in Punjab (Pakistan) Category:Jhelum District
